Package it.cnr.isti.hpc.dexter.cli.graph

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    GetNeighbourCategoryNodesCLI
    Given an entity (category) ID or a entity (category) label as input, and a direction (in/out) returns the categories linking to the given entity (in) or the categories linked from the given entity (out).
    GetNeighbourEntityCategoryNodesCLI
    Given an entity (category) ID or a entity (category) label as input, and a direction (in/out) returns the categories linking to the given entity (in) or the categories linked from the given entity (out).
    GetNeighbourNodesCLI
    Given an entity ID or a entity label as input, and a direction (in/out) returns the entities linking to the given entity (in) or the entities linked from the given entity (out).
    IndexIncomingCategoryNodesCLI

    IndexIncomingEntityCategoryNodesCLI
    IndexIncomingEntityCategoryNodesCLI generate the binary file containing the incoming entities for a category.
    IndexIncomingNodesCLI

    IndexOutcomingCategoryNodesCLI

    IndexOutcomingEntityCategoryNodesCLI

    IndexOutcomingNodesCLI
    IndexOutcomingNodesCLI generate the binary file containing the incoming entities.
